{"parse":{"title":"yep","pageid":62962,"redirects":[],"wikitext":"{{also|Yep|YEP}}\n==English==\n\n===Etymology===\nRepresenting {{m|en|yeah}} pronounced with the {{l|en|[[mouth]] [[snapped]] [[closed]]}} at the end. Compare {{m|en|yup}}, {{m|en|nope}}, {{m|en|welp}}, and {{m|en|ope}}. Compare also {{cog|de|jap|t=yep}}.\n\n===Pronunciation===\n* {{IPA|en|/jɛp/|[jɛp̚]|[jɛʔ]|[jɛʔp̚]}}\n* {{audio|en|LL-Q1860 (eng)-Vealhurl-yep.wav|a=Southern England}}\n* {{audio|en|LL-Q1860 (eng)-Wodencafe-yep.wav|a=US}}\n* {{rhymes|en|ɛp|s=1}}\n\n===Interjection===\n{{en-intj}}\n\n# {{lb|en|informal}} {{cap|yes}}.\n#: {{syn|en|Thesaurus:yes}}\n#: {{ant|en|nope}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|informal \"yes\"}}\n* Arabic: {{t|ar|أَيْوَة}} {{qualifier|Eastern Arabic}}, {{t|ar|إِيَّة}} {{qualifier|Western Arabic}}, {{t+|ar|آ}} {{qualifier|Egyptian Arabic}}\n* Catalan: {{t|ca|sip}}\n* Chinese:\n*: Mandarin: {{t+|cmn|是啊|tr=shì a}}, {{t|cmn|對啊|tr=duì a}}, {{t+|cmn|啊|tr=à}}, {{t+|cmn|嗯|tr=ǹg}}\n* Czech: {{t+|cs|jo}}\n* Danish: {{t|da|jep}}\n* Finnish: {{t+|fi|joo}}, {{t+|fi|juu}}, {{t+|fi|jep}}\n* French: {{qualifier|France}} {{t+|fr|ouaip}}, {{t+|fr|mouais}}, {{t+|fr|moui}}, {{t+|fr|voui}} {{qualifier|Quebec}} {{t+|fr|ouin}}\n* German: {{t+|de|jo}}\n* Hungarian: {{t+|hu|ja}}\n* Italian: {{t+|it|già}}\n* Japanese: {{t+|ja|うん|tr=un}}, {{t+|ja|そう|tr=sō}}, {{t+|ja|ええ|tr=ē}}, {{t+|ja|ああ|tr=ā}}\n* Korean: {{t+|ko|응}}, {{t+|ko|어}}, {{t|ko|넵}}\n* Latin: {{t+|la|etiam}}\n* Maltese: {{t|mt|ijwa}}, {{t|mt|ijja}}, {{t|mt|eħe}}\n* Norwegian:\n*: Bokmål: {{t|nb|jepp}}\n*: Nynorsk: {{t|nn|jepp}}\n* Persian: {{t+|fa|آره|tr=âre}}\n* Polish: {{t+|pl|no}}, {{t+|pl|ta}}\n* Portuguese: {{t+|pt|aham}}\n* Romanian: {{t+|ro|mda}}, {{t+|ro|dap}}\n* Russian: {{t+|ru|ага́|tr=agá, ahá}}, {{t+|ru|угу́|tr=ugú, uhú}}, {{t+|ru|так}}, {{t+|ru|ну}}\n* Spanish: {{t+|es|sip}}\n* Swedish: {{t|sv|jäpp}}, {{t+|sv|jepp}}, {{t+|sv|japp}}\n* Vietnamese: {{t+|vi|ừ}}, {{t+|vi|ờ}}\n{{trans-bottom}}\n\n===Noun===\n{{en-noun}}\n\n# {{lb|en|informal}} Yes.\n#: {{ux|en|I'll take that as a '''yep''', then.}}\n\n====Descendants====\n* {{desc|nb|jepp|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|nn|jepp|bor=1}}\n\n===Anagrams===\n* {{anagrams|en|a=epy|pye|pey|Pye}}\n\n{{cln|en|3-letter words}}"}}